Nemesis Enforcer:




Nemesis in his bat mode hovered in the air, his thirty foot wingspan flapping 
up an down to keep him in the air, though not really needed with his 
boosters.  "Woah, those mercenaries have lost it." He smiled mischeviously.  
"I wonder if I should help them..."
